ecomap
======

A turbogears application that provides auth and persistence for the ecomap (now known as social network map (ssnm)).

This codebase now also powers hope-ny, which is ssnm w/ an alternative skin


TESTING
=======

to run the unit tests, do:

   % nosetests
   
to start the server, in development:

* the very first time run start.sh to initialize the working env
* after that, for each session
  % source ./working-env/bin/activate
* then
  % python ./ecomap_start --mode <config file, w/out the .cfg extension> 